content.rendered:
Technical Services Engineer | Tulsa, Oklahoma

  • Full-Time Position
  • Will provide the customer with knowledge and skills to properly install and operate wireless systems
  • Will include some traveling to the customer site
  • Must have a minimum of 3 years of field experience with controls and instrumentation
  • Preferably experience related to equipment applications in Natural Gas Compression Industry
  • Experience with wireless radio communications technology preferred
  • Knowledge of industrial engine and driven equipment required
  • Bachelor’s degree in Electrical Engineering preferred, Associate in Electronics Engineering Technology will be considered with experience
  • $55,000-$60,000/year
